No offense, but some of you are idiots.  When you launch the keygen, left click and drag to the right to capture the entire serial.  Then copy it to your clipboard.  When you launch the program, put in the name/key.  It will say that it's an invalid key...just hit cancel.  

Then go into the folder with the key gen and copy the bryce.exe and paste it into the directory you installed the program.  Launch the program and enjoy.
